ZH:  为了完成任务，我们必须努力工作。
EN: In order to complete the task, we must work hard.

ZH: 她为了家人的幸福而牺牲了很多。
EN: She sacrificed a lot for the happiness of her family.

ZH: 为了环保，我们应该减少使用塑料袋。
EN: For environmental protection, we should reduce the use of plastic bags.

ZH: 这个决定是为了公司的利益做出的。
EN: This decision was made for the benefit of the company.

ZH: 他们为了追求更高的学历而努力学习。
EN: They study hard in order to pursue higher education.

ZH: 为了安全起见，请系好安全带。
EN: For safety reasons, please fasten your seatbelt.

ZH: 她为了爱情不惜放弃了自己的事业。
EN: She gave up her career for the sake of love.

ZH: 为了实现梦想，我们必须努力奋斗。
EN: In order to achieve our dreams, we must strive hard.

ZH: 他为了帮助别人而毫不犹豫地伸出援手。
EN: He reached out to help others without hesitation.

ZH: 为了保护动物，我们应该杜绝盗猎行为。
EN: To protect animals, we should eliminate poaching.

ZH: 他们为了升职加薪而努力工作。
EN: They work hard in order to get promoted and get a raise.

ZH: 为了保持健康，我们每天都要运动。
EN: In order to stay healthy, we need to exercise every day.

ZH: 我们为了实现共同的目标而团结一致。
EN: We unite in order to achieve a common goal.

ZH: 她为了弥补以前的失误而努力改进。
EN: She strives to improve in order to make up for past mistakes.

ZH: 为了捍卫自己的权益，我们应该奋起抗议。
EN: In order to defend our rights, we should protest.

ZH: 他们为了追求名利而不择手段。
EN: They resort to any means in order to pursue fame and fortune.

ZH: 为了提高工作效率，我们应该合理分配任务。
EN: To improve work efficiency, we should allocate tasks reasonably.

ZH: 他为了让家人过上更好的生活而拼尽全力工作。
EN: He works hard to ensure his family has a better life.

ZH: 为了展示自己的才能，她决定参加比赛。
EN: In order to showcase her talent, she decided to participate in the competition.

ZH: 我们为了创造美好的未来而共同努力。
EN: We work together in order to create a better future.
